Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, do you want a caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:37.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:38.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.35,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.75,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello. Are your parents around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.09,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:44.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm Kusakabe! We've just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.98,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.82,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.46,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.10,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, there's a bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Fish too! See that flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.23,Defalut,,0,0,0,,So, you like it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.30,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, it's terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.88,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Look, a tunnel of trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.54,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Is that our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.52,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's a wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Looks like a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.37,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,And it's all rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.75,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's gonna fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.16,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Look, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.83,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's a huge tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's a camphor tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:18.42,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Camphor tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.61,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.16,Defalut,,0,0,0,,An acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:35.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.28,Defalut,,0,0,0,,One for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Out of the way. I can't open the screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.62,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Acorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There are acorns in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They dropped from up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.11,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are squirrels in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.36,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Squirrels, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Or rats that like acorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have squirrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where shall I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:23.98,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll get the door for you. Satsuki, open up the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's just round the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.16,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Bathtubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's something in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:41.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A squirrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:46.78,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dunno. A bunch of black things but not roaches or mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.44,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:00.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Can you see 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I think they were... dustbunnies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,'Dustbunnies'? Like in my picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.88,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ghosts don't come out on days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,When you walk into a dark room from outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.10,Defalut,,0,0,0,,your eyes dim and so the dustbunnies come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:30.46,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come here, dustbunnies. Come out, come out, wherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:40.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work! See if you can find how to get upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Get up there and open all the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.35,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.07,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.56,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.20,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.35,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dustbunnies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Another acorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:04.01,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come out, dustbunnies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:47.16,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you there, Mr. Dustbunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:16.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, there's definitely something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:22.95,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's exciting! I've always wanted to live in a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:15.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I got it. Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.45,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You're full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:46.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,This is 'Nanny'. She looks after the house and came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm Satsuki and this is my sister, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:14:00.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'd have cleaned up if I'd known you'd be this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, you've done plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:08.28,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Lately I've been so busy in the rice paddies, I only did a bit of dusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What have you done to your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The dustbunny got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Your feet, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.88,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mine are black, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That must be the 'soot spreaders'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:40.57,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Those little, black, fuzzy things that fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:45.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's right. They breed in empty old houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:49.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,and cover them with soot and dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:57.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I could see them when I was little. Now you can too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are they like goblins or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:03.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Naah, nothing so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:09.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,If you keep smiling, they'll soon leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:16.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They're probably deciding where to go next, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, they're going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:23.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What happens if a huge one comes out, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.11,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.11,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I won't walk you to the bathroom at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:39.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay, cleaning time. Could you get some water from the stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,From the stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Did you get a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nanny, it's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:17.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Good, keep pumping 'til the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Huh... my Mom... for Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:28.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You live in a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.19,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I did the same when I was his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:48.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I hate boys. But I really love Nanny's rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.42,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, the house is going to fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.54,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I hope not. We've only just moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's laugh to keep the bogeymen away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,l'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.79,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I mean it. I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on, keep up the good work...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay! Washing... finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.50,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nanny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hard at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where're you all heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,To visit Mommy in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:54.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's nice. Give her my regards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.08,Defalut,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:42.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:44.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:47.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:49.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,So glad you came, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:52.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy took the wrong road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:55.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Really? Hello, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:57.12,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's a school holiday, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:01.34,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy is talking to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:03.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's so good to see you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Have you settled into the new house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.37,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:16.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mom, do you like ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:20.61,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Of course I do! I can't wait to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See, I told you Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:26.78,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei was worried that you wouldn't like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:28.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:30.88,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.95,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you fixing Mei's hair, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.56,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's really good. Lucky girl, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But she always gets mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.09,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's 'cuz you won't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:47.09,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come here, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Isn't yours too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:50.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, I like it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Do mine, Mommy! Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:53.82,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:59.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wavy hair, just like mine when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:03.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Will it be like yours when I grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:07.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Probably. You take after your Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:27.26,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mom looked really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:31.07,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You're right. The doctor says she'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:33.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Soon? Like tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.72,0:24:35.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You always say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:37.52,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is a little too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.35,0:24:41.29,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mom said she'll sleep with me in my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:45.82,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Weren't you saying you're big enough to sleep alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mom is special!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:12.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, time to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.76,0:25:19.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:26.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I overslept again...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:28.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I've got to bring a box lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:30.59,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.11,0:25:33.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I've made something for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:34.70,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.70,0:25:35.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,l'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.49,0:25:41.01,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:42.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:45.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, sit down and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:49.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here, wrap yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.51,0:25:55.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.24,0:25:56.80,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:25:59.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:02.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You made a friend already?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.94,0:26:04.95,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.35,0:26:07.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's Michiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.36,0:26:10.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:14.28,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.28,0:26:16.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:18.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:21.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:34.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.01,0:26:37.80,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Do I look all grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:40.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes dear. And where might you be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.14,0:26:42.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm just going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.29,0:27:06.50,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy, is it lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.50,0:27:08.75,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:23.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You be the flower shop, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:41.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Tadpoles!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.43,0:28:02.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Got no bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.57,0:28:16.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.45,0:33:56.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Who are you? A big Dustbunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.56,0:34:27.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,To-to-ro? You're Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.82,0:34:34.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I bet you're Totoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.02,0:35:47.81,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.81,0:35:48.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay, catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.40,0:35:52.27,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.27,0:35:55.19,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hey there. Is it that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.19,0:35:57.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where's Mei? I'm off to Michiko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:36:00.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We haven't eaten yet. Is Mei in the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.54,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.84,0:36:21.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, I found her hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.87,0:36:48.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.87,0:36:52.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.00,0:36:55.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where's Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:56.59,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.59,0:36:59.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.48,0:37:03.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Were you dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.43,0:37:04.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Totoro was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.26,0:37:08.07,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You mean that troll in your picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.43,0:37:15.61,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He was all hairy with a big mouth like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.61,0:37:22.30,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There's a tiny one and a little one and a huge one like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:29.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There you are. Wow, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.41,0:37:31.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A great hiding place!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.92,0:37:35.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, Mei said she met a Totoro here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:36.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.13,0:37:38.44,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.64,0:37:48.35,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.14,0:37:51.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.90,0:37:55.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.02,0:37:56.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.73,0:37:59.19,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It went to a big tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.19,0:38:01.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't any other path.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.90,0:38:04.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.23,0:38:23.17,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But it's true! Totoro was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.76,0:38:24.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.99,0:38:35.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I know, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.06,0:38:37.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.77,0:38:43.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Neither of us think you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.53,0:38:48.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You probably met the king of this forest. You were very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.74,0:38:52.97,Defalut,,0,0,0,,He doesn't come out very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:56.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We should pay our respects at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:38:57.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Pay our respects?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.58,0:38:59.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,To this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.81,0:39:18.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, you're getting heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.90,0:39:20.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy, look! That camphor tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.78,0:39:22.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What a big tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.43,0:39:32.01,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.58,0:39:34.70,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Is that the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.62,0:39:38.08,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.93,0:39:51.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The hole has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.05,0:39:52.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.10,0:39:56.10,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The hole disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.10,0:39:58.54,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I told you he doesn't come to see us often.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.54,0:40:01.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But will he come again? I want to meet him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.27,0:40:05.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:07.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:15.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,This tree must have stood here for years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.05,0:40:19.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Trees and people used to be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.38,0:40:27.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I saw that tree and fell in love with the house. Hope Mom likes it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.47,0:40:30.80,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's pay our respects then get home for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:33.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes, I promised to go see Michiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.47,0:40:35.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.22,0:40:36.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.66,0:40:41.44,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank you for looking after Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.44,0:40:43.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.48,0:40:45.61,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Let's race home!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:47.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.49,0:40:50.15,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.57,0:40:53.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.49,0:40:55.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.83,0:41:00.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Mother, something amazing{\i0} {\i1}happened today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.17,0:41:04.50,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mei met a giant Totoro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.51,0:41:13.97,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm hoping to see him{\i0} {\i1}myself soon, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.17,0:41:47.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta, hurry up! You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.38,0:41:48.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.09,0:42:32.36,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:34.09,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.09,0:42:35.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.14,0:42:37.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:46.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What happened, Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.90,0:42:51.44,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. She insisted that she be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.94,0:42:56.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's Dad's day at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.49,0:42:59.51,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You promised to be a good girl at Nanny's.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.45,0:43:06.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I still have two more classes and Nanny's too busy for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.13,0:43:12.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She was good up 'til now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.51,0:43:21.70,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.45,0:43:34.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Since Satsuki's mother is in the hospital, I want you all to be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.04,0:43:43.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.66,0:43:44.97,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's Totoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.46,0:43:48.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, you should keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.63,0:43:49.67,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.69,0:44:02.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.01,0:44:04.56,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I can't stay after class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.56,0:44:06.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We'll let the teacher know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.60,0:44:08.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:11.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, it's going to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.69,0:44:12.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.57,0:44:22.12,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.38,0:44:34.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.22,0:44:41.55,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I won't cry. Aren't I good?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.10,0:44:46.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.89,0:44:52.62,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dear Guardian Spirit, let us stay until the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.94,0:45:37.15,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.46,0:45:59.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.67,0:46:02.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's got holes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.52,0:46:17.11,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy forgot his umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.11,0:46:18.62,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.07,0:46:23.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I said I forgot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.99,0:46:27.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What idiot forgets his umbrella on a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.74,0:46:29.26,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.26,0:46:31.83,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You broke it playing, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.83,0:46:33.12,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.47,0:46:47.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.06,0:46:53.83,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello Satsuki. Hi, Mei. Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.23,0:46:56.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about Mei today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.85,0:46:58.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Sorry we couldn't do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.19,0:47:02.36,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta lent us this umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.36,0:47:06.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,He did? A broken old thing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.53,0:47:08.78,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei was with me, so I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.78,0:47:12.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But I'm so sorry that Kanta got wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.43,0:47:17.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It probably cleaned him up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.79,0:47:19.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you off to meet your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.38,0:47:20.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.25,0:47:21.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What good girls you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.21,0:47:24.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.18,0:47:37.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.06,0:47:38.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:44.53,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.58,0:47:58.75,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:02.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,All right, drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.26,0:48:12.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy wasn't on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.60,0:48:16.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,He'll be on the next one. Why don't you wait at Nanny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.89,0:48:54.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.80,0:49:29.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.97,0:49:33.84,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I told you. Wanna go to Nanny's?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.01,0:49:37.78,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It won't be much longer. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.19,0:49:46.79,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.45,0:49:55.45,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.16,0:51:20.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you Totoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.38,0:51:32.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.80,0:51:39.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.47,0:51:42.57,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Take it, Mei's slipping off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.98,0:51:50.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hold it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.28,0:53:08.77,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Here's the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.34,0:54:19.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,He took Daddy's umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.14,0:54:34.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.65,0:54:35.75,Defalut,,0,0,0,,All right, drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.52,0:54:39.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The train was late and I missed the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.44,0:54:42.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Were you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.65,0:54:44.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We met him, Dad! He was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.91,0:54:46.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,And the cat bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.07,0:54:48.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.49,0:54:50.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It was huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.33,0:54:54.16,Defalut,,0,0,0,,With big eyes like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.29,0:54:59.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We met him! We met Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.84,0:55:01.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.10,0:55:14.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.53,0:55:26.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Mother, I can't tell you{\i0} {\i1}how excited I was today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.41,0:55:31.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the scariest, funniest day{\i0} {\i1}I've ever had.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.14,0:55:33.87,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Totoro gave us a lovely present...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.87,0:55:38.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...wrapped in bamboo leaves and{\i0} {\i1}tied with dragon whiskers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.38,0:55:43.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we opened it,{\i0} {\i1}it was full of magic nuts and seeds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.09,0:55:54.24,Defalut,,0,0,0,,'We decided to plant them in the garden to make a lovely forest.'
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.24,0:56:00.98,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they haven't sprouted yet.{\i0} {\i1}Mei sits there all day, waiting for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.00,0:56:05.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looks like a little crab.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.78,0:56:12.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nearly summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.66,0:56:17.01,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dearest, dear Mom, get well soon.{\i0} {\i1}Love, Satsuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.50,0:56:22.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Come on. Bed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.34,0:56:27.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Lights off!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.38,0:56:28.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.26,0:56:32.07,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do you think they will sprout tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.43,0:56:37.52,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Totoro would know. Night night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.36,0:57:27.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.71,0:57:47.73,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's where we planted the seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.93,0:59:22.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wow, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.76,1:00:40.74,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We're the wind!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.28,1:01:42.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There are no trees!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.91,1:01:49.55,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yessss!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.87,1:01:53.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.92,1:01:56.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.63,1:02:00.88,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.44,1:02:22.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusakabe! Telegram!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.41,1:02:29.12,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.88,1:02:38.17,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.32,1:02:43.80,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.68,1:02:47.78,Defalut,,0,0,0,,This one is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.98,1:02:58.52,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.52,1:03:00.02,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.24,1:03:09.45,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Your garden's a treasure house.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.08,1:03:12.47,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.54,1:03:21.27,Defalut,,0,0,0,,These should be cold now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.67,1:03:23.30,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.81,1:03:34.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.18,1:03:40.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The sun blessed these so they're really good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.44,1:03:41.79,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Would they help my Mom, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.44,1:03:47.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Of course. If she eats my vegetables, she'll get better right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.78,1:03:50.53,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She's supposed to be back next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.53,1:03:52.58,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She'll sleep in my bed!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.33,1:03:56.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,At last. That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.06,1:04:02.55,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But it's only for a couple of days. To get used to the new house.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.17,1:04:07.30,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I see. We'll feed her lots of vegetables, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.30,1:04:11.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'll give her this corn I picked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.05,1:04:12.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.27,1:04:14.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.40,1:04:24.61,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There was a telegram for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.61,1:04:25.53,Defalut,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.78,1:04:32.09,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad won't be back till late, what shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.58,1:04:35.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Open it, it might be important.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.08,1:04:42.81,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Please contact, Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.17,1:04:48.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's from Mom's hospital! Something's happened to her!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.51,1:04:52.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nanny! What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.72,1:04:56.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Do you know where your Dad is?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.93,1:05:00.27,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I know his office number, but we don't have a telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.27,1:05:04.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta, take her to use the phone in the main house!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.65,1:05:12.70,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei, stay here with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.75,1:05:23.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Stay with Nanny, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.16,1:06:04.39,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello, l'd like to make a long-distance call, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.79,1:06:09.38,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's Tokyo 31-1382.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.97,1:06:13.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,A cute girl, Kanta.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.51,1:06:18.81,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.10,1:06:24.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello, may I speak to Dad... er... Mr. Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.86,1:06:27.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's his daughter, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.78,1:06:33.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Daddy? It's me, Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.03,1:06:39.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's up? From the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.72,1:06:42.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, I'll call them right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.71,1:06:45.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.71,1:06:52.27,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0} {\i1}I'll check and call you right back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.72,1:06:55.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging up now, stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.72,1:07:01.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,May I stay here until he calls back?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.77,1:07:04.08,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Stay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.48,1:07:13.57,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.25,1:07:25.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, this corn is for my Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.89,1:07:30.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, it's my Mom's!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.35,1:07:52.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Listen Mei. Mom's not well so she's not coming home this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.90,1:07:54.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.36,1:07:58.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do. You don't want her to get worse, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.32,1:08:00.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.12,1:08:04.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's just for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.37,1:08:09.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,So you don't care if she dies, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.09,1:08:14.42,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Stop being silly! I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.48,1:08:26.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.15,1:08:33.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.15,1:09:04.45,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We should bring the washing in...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.45,1:09:11.56,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much, Satsuki. Nanny's here to help, so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.44,1:09:19.59,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Your Dad said he'll stop by the hospital to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.28,1:09:26.99,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's just a cold. She'll be back next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.46,1:09:35.23,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They said it was just a cold...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.21,1:09:37.81,Defalut,,0,0,0,,when she went into hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.42,1:09:41.32,Defalut,,0,0,0,,But what if she dies!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.32,1:09:43.34,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.93,1:09:46.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mom will...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.73,1:09:56.69,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Nobody would leave two pretty little girls like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.61,1:10:01.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,There, there. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.49,1:10:06.20,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'll be here until Daddy comes back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.08,1:10:51.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.51,1:11:06.80,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Did she come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.80,1:11:09.36,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she at the bus stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.60,1:11:13.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,That's strange. Where has she gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.14,1:11:17.98,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I was nasty to her, 'cause she was being silly...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.98,1:11:20.67,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's heading for the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.67,1:11:26.86,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The hospital? It would take a grown-up three hours!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.86,1:11:27.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'll go look!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.33,1:11:36.35,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta, hurry! Tell your dad that Mei is missing!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.19,1:11:48.19,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Stupid Mei. Always getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.11,1:12:07.13,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.07,1:12:13.70,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a little girl pass by? She's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.70,1:12:19.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so. I'm sure I would've noticed...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.04,1:12:21.81,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Maybe she wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.19,1:12:43.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she came this way?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.40,1:12:44.67,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.81,1:13:18.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.19,1:13:22.56,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Jerk! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.56,1:13:25.46,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my sister. Have you seen a little girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.28,1:13:27.34,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.78,1:13:31.34,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She's four. I think she's heading to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.95,1:13:33.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.41,1:13:38.85,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No. We just came from there... but we didn't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.96,1:13:41.72,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.79,1:13:44.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where have you come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.63,1:13:46.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,From Matsugo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.00,1:13:47.67,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Matsugo?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.67,1:13:49.23,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.72,1:13:52.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.31,1:14:04.91,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.48,1:14:08.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Kanta!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.49,1:14:10.49,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.49,1:14:12.15,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No. And you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.99,1:14:17.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dad and the others are looking for her. I'll go to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.41,1:14:19.29,Defalut,,0,0,0,,you go back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.29,1:14:23.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I guess she got lost on the way to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.67,1:14:26.48,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They found a sandal by the pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.72,1:14:36.64,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We're not sure if it's hers or not!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.70,1:14:55.36,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.79,1:15:31.04,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, please protect her and...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.40,1:15:33.95,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's too deep here, better search further away!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.95,1:15:36.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hey, are there any poles left?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.91,1:15:46.96,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Grandma, Satsuki's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.75,1:15:53.31,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Nanny!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.59,1:15:56.40,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Look, is it hers?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.73,1:16:06.66,Defalut,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.57,1:16:23.12,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank heavens, I was sure it was hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.12,1:16:26.08,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanny was jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.08,1:16:27.43,Defalut,,0,0,0,,It's not hers!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.79,1:16:29.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where's she gone then?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.71,1:16:31.29,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Let's start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.29,1:16:33.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We better hurry, it'll be dark soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.05,1:16:36.94,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate your help, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.94,1:16:39.01,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Could have been any of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.95,1:17:10.17,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Please, help me Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.17,1:17:15.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei is lost. It'll be dark soon. I'm sure she's scared somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:48.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Totoro!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.91,1:17:53.89,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei is lost and we can't find her!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.42,1:17:59.90,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She must be scared; please help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.18,1:18:03.68,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.32,1:19:04.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They can't see the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.55,1:19:53.10,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FOREST-SWAMP
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.10,1:19:54.60,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\an8}CEMETERY-SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.72,1:19:58.63,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MEI
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.33,1:20:18.14,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.61,1:20:29.05,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The trees are moving out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.24,1:21:08.57,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.25,1:21:24.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Mei!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.05,1:21:30.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.18,1:21:32.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.51,1:21:37.93,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You wanted to take the corn to Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.54,1:21:48.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\an8}HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.95,1:21:51.21,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Will you take us to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.28,1:21:55.95,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.84,1:22:09.52,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. They didn't need to send a telegram just for a cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.97,1:22:14.28,Defalut,,0,0,0,,The girls must be worried. I'm sorry to upset them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.60,1:22:17.39,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine. As long as you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.39,1:22:22.41,Defalut,,0,0,0,,We've all learned to cope. This'll just postpone the enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.10,1:22:27.65,Defalut,,0,0,0,,They've put up with it so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.65,1:22:30.67,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm especially sorry for Satsuki; she's been so patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.82,1:22:32.92,Defalut,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.70,1:22:37.83,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I'm going to spoil them for a while when I come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.83,1:22:38.76,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.29,1:22:48.25,Defalut,,0,0,0,,She's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.25,1:22:50.00,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.42,1:23:01.33,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.89,1:23:04.06,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.36,1:23:12.18,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.78,1:23:14.71,Defalut,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.49,1:23:19.03,Defalut,,0,0,0,,I could swear I just saw Satsuki and Mei laughing up in that tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.95,1:23:24.22,Defalut,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were. Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.22,1:23:28.23,Defalut,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For Mother
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.23,1:23:30.23,Defalut,,0,0,0,,
